title: 350. Cultural Revolution - 2022 Missouri Primary Election Results
itunes:title: 350. Cultural Revolution - 2022 Missouri Primary Election Results
description: In today's episode, Andy reacts to the 2022 Missouri Primary Election results. He explains what these results mean to our community, the importance of getting engaged locally, and the next step we need to take to get America where we need it to go.
